title: PRIME MINISTER’S VISIT TO THE PENTAGON (Prime Minister's Office of the Islamic Republic of Pakistan) ...
text: ( Source : Prime Minister's Office of the Islamic Republic of Pakistan ) Prime Minister Muhammad Nawaz Sharif visited the Pentagon today evening at the invitation of US Defence Secretary Ashton Carter , says a press release received here today
